profile: Green Leaf Tree Services Ltd. is a professional, family run business serving The Columbia Valley and area with offices in Golden BC and Windermere, BC. We provide tree pruning, tree removal, dangerous tree removal, land clearing, and tree health consultation services. We offer fast friendly service, ISA Certified Arborists, WCB certified fallers, quality work, and competitive rates.
